, we are able to recover the\n\\hi~ power spectra with an accuracy of $\\approx95-99\\%$ for the different test\nsets. For the predicted astrophysical parameters, we have achieved an accuracy\nof $\\approx~81-90\\%$ and $\\approx~50-60\\%$ for the test sets corrupted with\nthermal noise corresponding to the \\textsc{ska-1 low} and \\textsc{hera},\nrespectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Dec 2021 19:02:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Feb 2022 16:01:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-29"}
