 experimental data\nindicates that the simulations can quantitatively predict robotic motion.\nOverall, the theoretical and numerical tools presented in this paper can shed\nlight on the design and control of this class of articulated robots in granular\nor fluid media.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Dec 2021 22:40:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-30"}
