 colliding particles are\ngradually covered by the background excitations caused by random field.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Dec 2021 04:58:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Nov 2022 01:52:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-02"}
