y can\nbe used during data acquisition to provide fast timing of the arrival of the\nparticles for triggering and event selection.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Dec 2021 12:29:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-30"}
